data.description: Step into the 2-story foyer & fall in love w/ this amazing home - designed for entertaining & family gatherings.  Your home can be the neighborhood "hot spot" as guests mingle throughout the downstairs & onto the covered front porch or to the gorgeous backyard w/ awesome views of the lake.  Kitchen island & butler's pantry make serving a breeze.  Private home office or study downstairs & computer/homework area upstairs.  Huge gameroom w/ sink & built-ins for lots of fun.  Secondary bedrooms are split upstairs w/ two separate bathrooms...one being a Jack and Jill.  So many upgrades offered including surround sound, central vacuum, double crown molding, textured carpeting, Kentmore cabinetry, stainless appliances, gas cooktop w/ grill, multiple closets & built-in shelving, warm paint colors, art niches, architectural features including columns, transom windows, under cabinet lighting, & master shower w/ seat. Check out the night pics of the lake in virtual tour!
